el":"part of"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"recLuZtSmAO6erIsc","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"recjNRR60PAuFtjha","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"rec5dSSsOutWlH2fW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"rec00JYAbLHvQFwog","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"recN4jruK7QVakoJh","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"recUlW6Qk0RBmMe07","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"recdMHFSmu222VnJG","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"rec8bEdIqk6qrW3mt","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"recTgDuoerMyuEBbL","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuu5VuXwWkHBKBs","target":"recSF4lyBebGjJEXI","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recVIh7E9GB6tFUSG","ref":"Josh.3.1","text":"And Joshua rose early in the morning; and they removed from Shittim, and came to Jordan, he and all the children of Israel, and lodged there before they passed over.","year":-1451},{"id":"rec6PrlT1NNC8rdlZ","ref":"Josh.3.2","text":"And it came to pass after three days, that the officers went through the host;","year":-1451},{"id":"recOd1LnySpMCCPHj","ref":"Josh.3.3","text":"And they commanded the people, saying, When ye see the ark of the covenant of the LORD your God, and the priests the Levites bearing it, then ye shall remove from your place, and go after it.","year":-1451},{"id":"recIcjVFFE8taow7K","ref":"Josh.3.4","text":"Yet there shall be a space between you and it, about two thousand cubits by measure: come not near unto it, that ye may know the way by which ye must go: for ye have not passed this way heretofore.","year":-1451},{"id":"recg7IReQDUcP0vu3","ref":"Josh.3.5","text":"And Joshua said unto the people, Sanctify yourselves: for to morrow the LORD will do wonders among you.","year":-1451},{"id":"recktaXAciIgwIWLE","ref":"Josh.3.6","text":"And Joshua spake unto the priests, saying, Take up the ark of the covenant, and pass over before the people. And they took up the ark of the covenant, and went before the people.","year":-1451},{"id":"recErtKSTxKlF7j2S","ref":"Josh.3.7","text":"And the LORD said unto Joshua, This day will I begin to magnify thee in the sight of all Israel, that they may know that, as I was with Moses, so I will be with thee.","year":-1451},{"id":"recIpmcts3snI7DSm","ref":"Josh.3.8","text":"And thou shalt command the priests that bear the ark of the covenant, saying, When ye are come to the brink of the water of Jordan, ye shall stand still in Jordan.","year":-1451}]}
